'''斋格尔堡''' ([[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]]/[[印地语|印地语]]: जयगढ़ क़िला ， Jaigarh Fort)位于印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[斋浦尔|斋浦尔]]郊外 ，[[琥珀堡|琥珀堡]]附近的山顶<ref name="BruynBain2010">{{cite book|author1=Pippa de Bruyn|author2=Keith Bain|author3=David Allardice|author4=Shonar Joshi|title=Frommer's India|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HlqM2CR4vfUC&pg=PA521|accessdate=16 April 2011|date=1 March 2010|publisher=Frommer's|isbn=978-0-470-55610-8|pages=521–522|archive-date=2014-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105073033/http://books.google.com/books?id=HlqM2CR4vfUC&pg=PA521|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ruggles2008">{{cite book|author=D. Fairchild Ruggles|title=Islamic gardens and landscapes|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PgbjhGwfXBEC&pg=PA205|accessdate=16 April 2011|year=2008|publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press|isbn=978-0-8122-4025-2|pages=205–206|archive-date=2014-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105073041/http://books.google.com/books?id=PgbjhGwfXBEC&pg=PA205|dead-url=no}}</ref>。斋格尔堡由斋辛格二世建于1726年并以他命名<ref name="BruynBain2010"/><ref name="Ruggles2008"/><ref name=perch>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cs.utah.edu/~noliver/india/Forts/Jaigarh-AmberFort/Jaigarh.html|title=Jaigarh Fort – Jaipur, India|accessdate=14 April 2011|publisher=cs.utah.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311093126/http://www.cs.utah.edu/~noliver/india/Forts/Jaigarh-AmberFort/Jaigarh.html|archive-date=2014-03-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

该堡垒崎岖不平，结构设计与[[琥珀堡|琥珀堡]]相似。它沿南北方向的长度为3公里（1.9英里），宽度为1公里（0.62英里）。该堡垒有一门名为 "Jaivana"（Jaivana大炮）的大炮，它是在堡垒范围内制造，当时是世界上最大的轮式大炮。斋格尔堡和琥珀堡通过地下通道相连，被认为是一个综合体。<ref name="BruynBain2010"/><ref name=Jaivan>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jaipur.org.uk/forts-monuments/jaigarh-fort.html|title=Jaipur|accessdate=16 April 2011|publisher=Jaipur.org.uk|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615190554/https://www.jaipur.org.uk/forts-monuments/jaigarh-fort.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

